author: David Kelly
title: UA all over Beavers by 27 at the half
text:
UA all over Beavers by 27 at the half Posted: TUCSON, AZ (Tucson News Now) - 
The Arizona Wildcats have found their offense as the Cats lead Oregon State 34-7 at the half. 
Anu Solomon has returned to the starting lineup and thrown for 208 yards. 
Jared Baker has run for 83 yards on five carries. 
The Wildcats defense is playing well early with one takeaway and a big hit by Will Parks. 
We will have highlights and reaction coming up after the game on KOLD News 13 at 5:30 and later over on FOX 11 News at Nine.
